    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>※ 如果游戏运行过快或过慢，</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>请查看页面底部的“关于运行的注意事项”。</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >關於《閃攻機人阿修羅 - ASURA THE STRIKER -》</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >這是一款致敬80～90年代街機遊戲、充滿<strong>速度與暢快感的3D街機風格射擊遊戲！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你將成為人型戰鬥兵器「阿修羅」，迎擊來自宇宙的不斷侵略者。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>能量射擊（Energy Shot）</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>閃耀鐵拳（Shining Knuckle）</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>閃電超驅（Lightning Over Drive）</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >運用三種動作在戰場上奔馳戰鬥！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🎮 特色動作</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389830/extras/03e84eb18412cbea723237db1f3b61e4.poster.avif?t=1767716607\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389830/extras/03e84eb18412cbea723237db1f3b61e4.webm?t=1767716607\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389830/extras/03e84eb18412cbea723237db1f3b61e4.mp4?t=1767716607\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >殲滅成群結隊的侵略者。</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389830/extras/0588d2ee7c9fcf91ee13d34199e96d3f.poster.avif?t=1767716607\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389830/extras/0588d2ee7c9fcf91ee13d34199e96d3f.webm?t=1767716607\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389830/extras/0588d2ee7c9fcf91ee13d34199e96d3f.mp4?t=1767716607\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >用閃電超驅化解危機！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389830/extras/c83bf3c62eb91e4c1f8750fff75011fd.poster.avif?t=1767716607\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389830/extras/c83bf3c62eb91e4c1f8750fff75011fd.webm?t=1767716607\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389830/extras/c83bf3c62eb91e4c1f8750fff75011fd.mp4?t=1767716607\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >用閃耀鐵拳一擊擊破強敵！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389830/extras/99fd9409ee56de44848427813c0374ac.poster.avif?t=1767716607\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389830/extras/99fd9409ee56de44848427813c0374ac.webm?t=1767716607\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389830/extras/99fd9409ee56de44848427813c0374ac.mp4?t=1767716607\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >可怕的侵略者BOSS登場！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389830/extras/67223bb8bdab139f8acf3ecd61d72402.poster.avif?t=1767716607\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389830/extras/67223bb8bdab139f8acf3ecd61d72402.webm?t=1767716607\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389830/extras/67223bb8bdab139f8acf3ecd61d72402.mp4?t=1767716607\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🕹️ 基本操作</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>移動</strong>：左搖桿或方向鍵</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >(你可以在菜单中选择松开摇杆时，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >是让它回到中央还是停留在当前位置。)</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>能量射擊</strong>：按下射擊按鈕攻擊</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>閃耀鐵拳</strong>：長按拳擊按鈕 → 放開時攻擊</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>閃電超驅</strong>：按下減速按鈕可減緩時間（消耗能量條）</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🧪 關於開發者</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>「LeftOver」</strong> 是由兩位開發者組成的全新獨立品牌。  <br>企劃、程式、美術、音樂等，<strong>幾乎所有內容皆由兩人親手打造。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >雖然製作節奏較慢，但我們致力於打造最棒的遊戲體驗。  <br>敬請支持並加入願望清單！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>※ 关于运行的注意事项</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・目前使用刷新率超过60Hz的显示器时，可能会出现游戏运行过快或过慢的情况。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >遇到这种情况时，请尝试在游戏设置中关闭垂直同步（vSync）。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >OPTION → vSync → Off</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・目前仍在调整中，BGM和音效（SE）的音量设置已被锁定。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >预计将在下次更新中开放调整功能。</p>",
